nodes.text: Euraana Fall was a female Mawan who served as a liaison to Jedi Master Yaddle and Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi, and Anakin Skywalker, who were dispatched to Mawan by the Jedi High Council to help establish a peaceful government on the planet, three years before the First Battle of Geonosis.

Euraana's pink skin and blue veins earned her the respect and admiration of other members of the Mawan upper class. She greatly desired to restore Mawan to its former beauty, so much so that she was willing to work with the lower classes to achieve her goal.
